                      ],
                      "text": "Prologue: Songs of the Wind",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "After Barbatos founded his beloved city of Mondstadt, he left it to the care of its first residents and went on his way. Human greed, however, knew no bounds. The rich seized control over the city and ruled it the way they see fit. On the eve of the city's celebrated Ludi Harpastum, a mysterious bard came to the city...",
